<h1>Benefits of the Idaho Work Study Program:</h1>
<p></p>
<ul>
<li>Reimbursement from the State of Idaho through BYU-Idaho to help pay the students&rsquo; wages</li>
<li>Opportunity to hire students with ties to the state of Idaho</li>
<li>Enjoy employing students with current academic experience and the latest technological advances related to your industry</li>
</ul>
<h3>Eligibility</h3>
<p>In order to be eligible to receive compensation through the Idaho Work Study program, employers must fill out and turn in the following forms to the BYU-I Financial Aid Office:</p>
